{"tid":2411361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵：東鐵綫假衝燈次數近日減少　不影響列車安全","createTime":"2021-02-17T09:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T10:28:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b2546465ed32e4ac1a66a13b5d3c87af9afbc87","tid":2411361,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"港鐵表示，東鐵綫出現列車「假衝燈」的次數近日已減少，強調不影響列車安全。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵東鐵綫一個多星期前轉用新信號系統，並啟用九卡列車。港鐵指，在運作初期，已安排人手修正及調校新信號系統，當中包括發出不需要的警號，而不涉及有列車實際越過停車信號燈。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵指，由於舊信號系統在羅湖貨場、上水側綫及何東樓車廠等地方沒有配置相類警號，而新系統的相關配置和程序需要磨合及調校，在實施管控措施後，系統出現列車越過停車信號燈的不需要警號次數，近日已減少。工程人員已與承辦商緊密溝通、及早跟進及調校，強調有關情況不影響列車安全運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=424348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424348&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=a8cccfb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424348&h=9f2ae46d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=424348</a>"},{"pid":"91efa3f65ca1953e1c0e0b64bbe3b7cb639c2294","tid":2411361,"uid":101309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"調較=熄左咪冇衝燈囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e943ed7392986b9309f9f12821291328697f0346","tid":2411361,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3b6348e4e73a99cbdf7c7ffe559ec1f3cde291","tid":2411361,"uid":125017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:31:24.000Z","msg":"睇黎好快有追尾睇"},{"pid":"e805183c888a42b53e21462cae5a61ee53239457","tid":2411361,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"有撞車風險好正常<br />\n可選坐巴士"},{"pid":"33e3fb316027a24fdf5f60be45afd24128fa299f","tid":2411361,"uid":301529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T09:43:39.000Z","msg":"邊個警號響咪disable佢囉 咁都要教"},{"pid":"12a50ad39b427a89675941ab5ac96b0f3a9656d3","tid":2411361,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:28:57.000Z","msg":"變晒真衝燈"}]}